graph TD
    A["Layer 1: Ingestion<br/>Gmail OAuth + Email Scanning"] --> B["Layer 2: Parsing<br/>Amount, Merchant, Date Extraction"]
    B --> C["Layer 3: Processing<br/>Dedup, Normalize, Categorize"]
    C --> D["Layer 4: Storage<br/>PostgreSQL — Raw + Processed"]
    D --> E["Layer 5: Insights<br/>Category Spend, Trends, Recurring"]
    E --> F["Layer 6: Reporting<br/>Monthly Summary, CSV Export"]
    F --> G["Layer 7: Advanced (Future)<br/>Predictions, Anomaly Detection"]

