## 6. Dashboard & Insights

### Dashboard Components

| Component | Data Source | Update Frequency |
|-----------|-----------|-----------------|
| Transaction List | `transactions` table | Real-time |
| Monthly Total | `SUM(amount) WHERE month=current` | Per-sync |
| Category Breakdown | `GROUP BY category_id` | Per-sync |
| Top Merchants | `GROUP BY merchant, ORDER BY SUM(amount)` | Per-sync |
| Daily Trend | `GROUP BY transaction_date` | Per-sync |
| Insights Cards | Computed comparisons | Per-sync |
| Recurring Payments | Same merchant + amount + interval | Daily batch |

### Insight Generation Rules

| Insight Type | Logic |
|-------------|-------|
| Category % | `category_spend / total_spend * 100` |
| Top merchant | `MAX(SUM(amount) GROUP BY merchant)` |
| Spending trend | Compare current month vs previous month |
| Recurring detection | Same merchant + same amount ± 5% + interval 28–31 days |

### Sample Dashboard Output (5 Transactions)

| Merchant | Amount | Category |
|----------|--------|----------|
| Swiggy | ₹450 | Food |
| Amazon | ₹1,200 | Shopping |
| Uber | ₹230 | Travel |
| Netflix | ₹499 | Subscription |
| Electricity | ₹1,500 | Bills |

**Total:** ₹3,879

**Insights Generated:**
- "Bills are your highest expense category (39%)"
- "You have 1 active subscription (Netflix ₹499/mo)"
- "Food spending is moderate at 12%"

